  "detailed_description": "Under Stranger Stars is the story of one man ruining the entire universe armed with nothing but a small spaceship, a moderately homicidal AI and an absurd variety of guns. Inspired by <i>The Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy</i>, <i>Sunless Sea</i> and that one time the developer got a parking fine, Under Stranger Stars is a game of adventure and absurdity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070030/extras/1e8ea90ebd70c41129f29b4260d98eba.poster.avif?t=1566848353\" width=592 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070030/extras/1e8ea90ebd70c41129f29b4260d98eba.webm?t=1566848353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070030/extras/1e8ea90ebd70c41129f29b4260d98eba.mp4?t=1566848353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Discover</strong> an open world filled with stories, spaceports and enemies ready for you to uncover, investigate, and murder. Assassinate bounties, take on Dreadnoughts and hunt down mega-freighters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070030/extras/a8819ba4de988f6020629be917b09069.poster.avif?t=1566848353\" width=620 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070030/extras/a8819ba4de988f6020629be917b09069.webm?t=1566848353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1070030/extras/a8819ba4de988f6020629be917b09069.mp4?t=1566848353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
